high_descs: Turn left, take a step, turn right so you face the counter with the toaster on.
Pick up the egg behind the loaf of bread.
Turn left, walk three steps, turn left and walk to the sink.  Look up toward the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the egg inside, close the door and turn it on.  When it turns off, open the door, take out the egg and close the microwave door.
Turn completely around, take a step, turn right, move slightly forward, turn right so you are facing the counter on the left side of the sink.
Put the egg on the counter to the left of the green sponge in the front.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the egg and put it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to bread on counter
Pick up egg from behind bread
Put egg in microwave, cook egg, retrieve egg
Turn left, walk to coffee machine
Put egg on counter to the left of first sponge.
anns.task_desc: Get egg, cook it in microwave, take egg, place on counter by coffee machine.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter on the left.
Grab an egg from the counter.
Walk to the microwave behind you.
Place the egg in the microwave, then remove it.
Walk to the kitchen counter on the left of the microwave.
Put the egg on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg and put it on a counter.
